{"word":"Eagle","slug":"eagle","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Eagle</b> Forbidden as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=13'>Lev 11:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=12'>Deu 14:12</a><br/> Swift flight of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=28&verse=49'>Deu 28:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=9&verse=26'>Job 9:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=19'>Pro 30:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=13'>Jer 4:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=22'>Jer 49:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=4&verse=19'>Lam 4:19</a><br/> Nest of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=11'>Deu 32:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=39&verse=30'>Job 39:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=16'>Jer 49:16</a><br/> Bears her young on her wings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=4'>Exo 19:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=11'>Deu 32:11</a><br/> Long life of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=103&verse=5'>Psa 103:5</a><br/> Molting of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=1&verse=16'>Mic 1:16</a><br/> Gier-eagle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=18'>Lev 11:18</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=4'>Exo 19:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=11'>Deu 32:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=40'>Jer 48:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=1'>Hos 8:1</a><br/> Symbolic<br/